docs {
  # Get My Organizations
  
  Returns **all organizations** where the current user has access.
  
  ## Authentication Required
  - HTTP-only cookie with access token
  
  ## Response
  Returns an array of organizations with details:
  ```json
  {
    "success": true,
    "message": "Organizations retrieved successfully",
    "data": [
      {
        "org_id": 1,
        "org_name": "Acme Corporation",
        "role": "org_owner",
        "org_active": true,
        "role_active": true,
        "assigned_at": "2025-10-27T10:00:00Z",
        "email": "contact@acme.com",
        "phone": "+90 212 555 0001",
        "address": "123 Business Street"
      },
      {
        "org_id": 2,
        "org_name": "Tech Solutions",
        "role": "org_admin",
        "org_active": true,
        "role_active": true,
        "assigned_at": "2025-10-26T15:30:00Z"
      }
    ],
    "count": 2
  }
  ```
  
  ## Use Cases
  - **Organization switcher UI** - Show all orgs user can access
  - **Dashboard initialization** - List available workspaces
  - **Multi-tenant navigation** - Switch between organizations
  - **Role-based feature access** - Check permissions per org
  
  ## Multi-Organization Support
  - One user can belong to **multiple organizations**
  - Each organization has a different role (owner, admin, manager, user, viewer)
  - Ordered by most recently assigned first
  - Only shows active organizations and active roles
}
